# Revo Olympics Repository

Monorepo: `revoolympics`

## Layout

- `apps/player_app/` — Flutter player (main user app)
- `apps/admin_web/` — Flutter Web admin
- `apps/spectator_hub/` — Version 5 placeholder only
- `unity/shared_bridge/` — Flutter–Unity WebGL bridge (shared)
- `unity/game_templates/` — portrait and landscape templates
- `unity/games/` — individual Unity WebGL games
- `firebase/` — Functions, Firestore, Storage, Hosting, seed
- `tools/` — webgl_validator, build_publisher, localization_validator
- `docs/product/` — authoritative product rules

## Architecture (fixed)

- Flutter is the player application; Unity WebGL runs inside WebView
- Official results validated by Cloud Functions only
- No secrets in Git, Flutter assets, Unity Resources, or docs

## Commits

Use `type(scope): description` — see CONTRIBUTING.md

## Scope

Match work to the active sprint. Do not implement features from later versions without explicit approval.
